OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1774915371
OL,3,CSocial media ban for under-16s 'not
OL,4,Cthe right approach', says Google UK
OL,5,Cboss
OL,7,FA ban on social media for under-16s is
OL,8,Fnot the "right approach" and could
OL,9,Fpush children towards more dangerous
OL,10,Fand unsupervised corners of the
OL,11,Finternet, Google's UK boss has warned.
OL,13,FKate Alessi, managing director and
OL,14,Fvice-president of Google UK and
OL,15,FIreland, told the Press Association
OL,16,Fthe tech giant ` which owns YouTube `
OL,17,Fis not supportive of "blanket bans" as
OL,18,Fthe Government faces mounting calls to
OL,19,Fstop children having access to social
OL,20,Fmedia.
OL,26,@pD@IOUpD@XO]yD@VOUyD@cO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
