OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1774915371
OL,3,CSocial media ban for under-16s 'not
OL,4,Cthe right approach', says Google UK
OL,5,Cboss
OL,7,FPrime Minister Sir Keir Starmer
OL,8,Fsignalled at the weekend he was
OL,9,Fprepared to take action to curb
OL,10,Ffeatures that keep young people
OL,11,Faddicted to social media, with the
OL,12,FGovernment currently consulting on an
OL,13,Foutright ban for under-16s.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1774915371
OL,3,CSocial media ban for under-16s 'not
OL,4,Cthe right approach', says Google UK
OL,5,Cboss
OL,7,FA landmark court case in the US last
OL,8,Fweek saw Facebook owner Meta and
OL,9,FGoogle found liable for a woman's
OL,10,Fchildhood social media addiction
OL,11,Fthrough deliberately designing
OL,12,Faddictive products, and ordered to pay
OL,13,Fdamages of six million US dollars
OL,14,F(#4.6 million) between them.
OL,16,FMs Alessi said Google does not agree
OL,17,Fwith the verdict and plans to appeal.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1774915371
OL,3,CSocial media ban for under-16s 'not
OL,4,Cthe right approach', says Google UK
OL,5,Cboss
OL,7,FShe said a social media ban is not the
OL,8,Fanswer to children's online wellbeing
OL,9,Fand cautioned if countries such as the
OL,10,FUK followed the lead of Australia,
OL,11,Fwhich introduced a world-first social
OL,12,Fmedia ban for under-16s in December,
OL,13,Fit could have unintended consequences.
OL,15,FMs Alessi told PA: "We don't believe
OL,16,Fthat's the right approach.
OL,18,F"We believe blanket bans take choices
OL,19,Faway from parents and push kids out of
OL,20,Fsupervised spaces."
OL,26,@wD@TOUzD@AOU|D@SO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1774915371
OL,3,CSocial media ban for under-16s 'not
OL,4,Cthe right approach', says Google UK
OL,5,Cboss
OL,7,FBut she said it was important that
OL,8,F"appropriate guardrails" are in place,
OL,9,Fwith YouTube recently introducing
OL,10,Ffeatures to help prevent addictive
OL,11,Fbehaviours in children and teenagers,
OL,12,Fsuch as timers for its Shorts format,
OL,13,Fas well as customised "Bedtime" and
OL,14,F"Take a break" functions.
OL,16,F"We want to make sure our products are
OL,17,Fbuilt to be as safe as possible," Ms
OL,18,FAlessi said.
OL,26,@pD@AOUpD@XO]uD@WOUuD@_O]vD@AOUvD@NO]xD@
OL,26,AAOUyD@aO]
