OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1774915371
OL,3,CSocial media ban for under-16s 'not
OL,4,Cthe right approach', says Google UK
OL,5,Cboss
OL,7,F"We'll work with Government and
OL,8,Fcontinue to partner with them as they
OL,9,Fwork through this," she added.
OL,11,FThe comments come as Google announced
OL,12,Fits latest community programme to
OL,13,Fboost artificial intelligence (AI)
OL,14,Fknowledge and skills to help Britons
OL,15,Fprogress professionally.
OL,26,@oD@AOUqD@SO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
