PN,30207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1774915371
OL,3,CSocial media ban for under-16s 'not
OL,4,Cthe right approach', says Google UK
OL,5,Cboss
OL,7,FIt is launching pop-up hubs across the
OL,8,FUK to train people on how to get the
OL,9,Fbest out of AI, including "quick win"
OL,10,Fdemos on areas such as how to automate
OL,11,Fadmin tasks and use agentic tools to
OL,12,Fcarry out tasks and research, as well
OL,13,Fas guides on building a social media
OL,14,Fpresence.
OL,16,FThe pop-up hubs ` called Squeeze the
OL,17,FJuice bars ` will be based in Leeds,
OL,18,FLiverpool and Birmingham and the
OL,19,FGovernment's so-called AI Growth Zones
OL,20,Fin Oxfordshire, the North East, Wales
OL,21,Fand Lanarkshire.
OL,26,@qD@[OUqD@eO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1774915371
OL,3,CSocial media ban for under-16s 'not
OL,4,Cthe right approach', says Google UK
OL,5,Cboss
OL,7,FThe firm is also launching a tour of
OL,8,Funiversity campuses nationwide, while
OL,9,Fit has earmarked nearly #2 million in
OL,10,Ffunding through its Google.org
OL,11,Fcharitable arm to help fund AI
OL,12,Finitiatives run by social enterprise
OL,13,Fgroup Inco, children's charity Chance
OL,14,Fand the Good Things Foundation.
OL,16,FGoogle hopes the programme will
OL,17,F"uplevel" AI use, with recent research
OL,18,Fcommissioned by the firm showing only
OL,19,Fa quarter of AI users believe they are
OL,20,Fgetting significant value and only one
OL,21,Fin 10 see themselves as advanced users.
OL,26,@yD@AOUyD@IO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
