FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30209
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1774915371
OL,3,CSocial media ban for under-16s 'not
OL,4,Cthe right approach', says Google UK
OL,5,Cboss
OL,7,FMs Alessi said: "Unlocking real value
OL,8,Fmeans moving beyond basic adoption to
OL,9,F'squeeze the juice' from these tools.
OL,11,F"With AI Works for Britain, we'll
OL,12,Fbring practical AI skills to people in
OL,13,Fevery corner of the UK ` from juice
OL,14,Fbars to Jobcentres ` to help them use
OL,15,FAI to achieve their goals."
OL,26,@oD@QOUsD@AOUwD@[O]
